change in the name

00:02:46.475 --> 00:02:50.211
is to reflect the slight change
in the direction of the game.

00:02:50.211 --> 00:02:52.460
One of the new elements we've
added as a win condition

00:02:52.460 --> 00:02:55.830
is collecting an entire
set of hardcore armor

00:02:55.830 --> 00:02:59.010
to be the hardcore-est
dragon in the land.

00:02:59.010 --> 00:03:01.950
And so we're intending
on adding a little bit

00:03:01.950 --> 00:03:03.620
of a cheeky, funny,
dialogue flair

00:03:03.620 --> 00:03:05.495
to the game to make it
a little less serious.

00:03:08.110 --> 00:03:10.170
