main concept of our game

00:03:10.170 --> 00:03:13.200
is that you're a dragon,
and you have a horde of gold

00:03:13.200 --> 00:03:15.780
that you are protecting
and also trying to grow.

00:03:15.780 --> 00:03:19.660
