00:59:01.723 --> 00:59:05.290
solve it using some
other weapon as well.

00:59:05.290 --> 00:59:07.190
The crowbar happens
to be an iconic weapon

00:59:07.190 --> 00:59:08.700
of the Half-Life series.

00:59:08.700 --> 00:59:12.440
And so they just assume, you're
getting into Half-Life 2,

00:59:12.440 --> 00:59:14.960
you probably realize
that the crowbar

00:59:14.960 --> 00:59:18.170
